## 12. RECOMMENDED BUILD ORDER

### Sprint A — Fix the worst stubs (3-4 days)
Agents page rebuild — Fleet view + machine groups + SSH
Skill Workshop — Per-agent training interfaces
Production Calendar — Calendar grid with content cards
Trend Radar — Isaac's trend detection feed

### Sprint B — Analytics & Revenue (2-3 days)
YouTube Analytics — Per-video + channel metrics
Social Analytics — Cross-platform performance
Consulting CRM — Lead/deal pipeline
Cinematic Sites — Project tracking board

### Sprint C — Knowledge & Content depth (2-3 days)
Brain & Wiki — Force-directed graph + visibility filters
Office — Per-workspace rooms + meeting state
Asset Lab — Type filters + masonry grid
Short Pipeline + Shorts — Kanban + per-platform queues

### Sprint D — Global system polish (2-3 days)
Sidebar live badges — Count badges on all nav items
Global search command box — "Ask Henry or jump anywhere"
Agent personality baselines — 13 agent MEMORY.md → system prompts
Inbox — Contact intelligence panel + Inbox Zero
Idea Feed — Promote-to-pipeline + cross-linking

### Sprint E — Remaining pages (1-2 days)
People page — Memory-integrated directory
Projects page — Portfolio with links
Docs/Logs pages — Flesh out
Hardware/Runtime — Fleet view (shared with Agents page)
Org Chart — Skill Workshop band + workspace colors

